'''國民戲院'''（[[英語|英語]]譯名：{{lang|en|'''P.O.P Cinema'''}}）是2003年由[[行政院文化建設委員會|行政院文化建設委員會]]與[[行政院新聞局|行政院新聞局]]結合地方資源的[[電影|電影]]映演計畫。<ref name="multiple">{{Cite web |url = http://www.funscreen.com.tw/headline.asp?H_No=462 |title = 熄燈一年，整裝再出發—國民戲院十年回顧與展望 |author = 洪健倫 |date = 2013-05-27 |publisher = 財團法人國家電影中心 , 放映週報 , funscreen-No.409 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-03-11 |archive-date = 2019-06-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190603013804/http://www.funscreen.com.tw/headline.asp?H_No=462 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 國民戲院計畫起跑 北歐影展打頭陣 | publisher = 中央通訊社 | url = http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/3/3/13/n286158.htm | date = 2003-03-13 | author = 吳素柔 | accessdate = 2015-08-23 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2019-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190605230935/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/3/3/13/n286158.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

